 Distribution passes\n\n### Vectorization and Backend Passes (lines 1750-1850):\n1. `addVectorPasses()` - Loop and SLP vectorization\n2. `LoopSinkPass()`\n3. `InstSimplifyPass()`\n4. `DivRemPairsPass()`\n5. `TailCallElimPass()`\n6. `SimplifyCFGPass()`\n\n### Final Global Optimizations (lines 1850-1900):\n1. `AllocTokenPass()`\n2. `HotColdSplittingPass()`\n3. `IROutlinerPass()`\n4. `GlobalDCEPass()`\n5. `ConstantMergePass()`\n6. `MergeFunctionsPass()` (if enabled)\n7. `CGProfilePass()`\n8. `RelLookupTableConverterPass()`\n9. `WholeProgramDevirtPass()` with devirtualization\n\n## 7. Static Pass Registry\n\nAll passes are catalogued in `llvm/lib/Passes/PassRegistry.def`, which defines:\n- MODULE_ANALYSIS: Module-level analysis passes\n- MODULE_PASS: Module-level transformation passes\n- CGSCC_ANALYSIS/CGSCC_PASS: Call graph SCC passes\n- FUNCTION_ANALYSIS/FUNCTION_PASS: Function-level passes\n- LOOP_ANALYSIS/LOOP_PASS: Loop-level passes\n\nThis file is included by PassBuilder to generate the pass registration and parsing infrastructure.\n\n## 8. Execution Flow\n\n1. **Initialization**: At startup, all passes call their INITIALIZE_PASS functions, registering themselves in PassRegistry\n2. **Pipeline Selection**: Frontend calls PassBuilder::buildPerModuleDefaultPipeline() with optimization level\n3. **Pipeline Construction**: PassBuilder methods construct nested PassManager objects, calling addPass() to add passes\n4. **Pipeline Execution**: ModulePassManager::run() is called with the module and AnalysisManager\n5. **Pass Execution**: Each pass is run sequentially via its operator()(Module&, ModuleAnalysisManager&)\n6. **Analysis Invalidation**: After each pass, the AnalysisManager invalidates analyses based on PreservedAnalyses\n\n## Key Integration Points\n\n- **PassManager Template** (`llvm/include/llvm/IR/PassManager.h`): Core template-based execution engine\n- **PassRegistry** (`llvm/include/llvm/PassRegistry.h/cpp`): Central pass metadata repository\n- **PassBuilder** (`llvm/include/llvm/Passes/PassBuilder.h`): High-level pipeline construction API\n- **PassBuilderPipelines.cpp** (`llvm/lib/Passes/PassBuilderPipelines.cpp`): Implementation of optimization pipelines\n- **PassSupport.h** (`llvm/include/llvm/PassSupport.h`): Macros for pass registration\n- **PassRegistry.def** (`llvm/lib/Passes/PassRegistry.def`): Static declaration of all built-in passes"
